{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":560,"text":"We all have milestones in life\nthat we remember so vividly."},{"time":5000,"text":"The first one for me\nwas when I was entering kindergarten."},{"time":8640,"text":"My big brother was in school,\nand by golly, it was my time."},{"time":13000,"text":"And I went trottin' down that hallway."},{"time":15280,"text":"I was so excited, I almost wet myself."},{"time":18520,"text":"And I go to the door,"},{"time":20120,"text":"and there was the teacher\nwith a warm welcome,"},{"time":22760,"text":"and she took me into the classroom,"},{"time":24920,"text":"showed me my little cubbyhole --"},{"time":26520,"text":"we all remember those\nlittle cubbyholes, don't we --"},{"time":29160,"text":"and we put our stuff in there."},{"time":31240,"text":"And then she said, \"Go over to the circle"},{"time":33240,"text":"and play with the kids\nuntil class starts.\""},{"time":36160,"text":"So I went over there\nand plopped down like I owned the place,"},{"time":39640,"text":"and I'm playing,"},{"time":41080,"text":"and all of a sudden, the boy next to me,"},{"time":43009,"text":"he was wearing a white shirt\nwith blue shorts."},{"time":46080,"text":"I remember it like it was yesterday."},{"time":48840,"text":"Suddenly he stopped playing and he said,"},{"time":51520,"text":"\"Why are you so short?\""},{"time":53920,"text":"And I just kept playing.\nI didn't think he was talking to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57880,"text":"And in a louder voice, he said,"},{"time":59720,"text":"\"Hey, why are you so short?\""},{"time":62600,"text":"So I looked up and I said,"},{"time":64040,"text":"\"What are you talking about?\nLet's just play. We're happy."},{"time":67760,"text":"I've been waiting for this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":69920,"text":"And so we played,\nand about a minute later,"},{"time":72120,"text":"the girl next to him,\nin a white shirt and a pink skirt,"},{"time":75800,"text":"stood up, put her hands on her hips,"},{"time":77560,"text":"and said, \"Yeah,\nwhy do you look so different?\""},{"time":81560,"text":"And I went, \"What are you talking about?"},{"time":84480,"text":"I don't look different. I'm not short.\nAgain, let's just play.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":88520,"text":"About this time, I looked\nall around the circle I was in,"},{"time":92040,"text":"and all the kids had stopped playing\nand they were all looking at me."},{"time":96120,"text":"And I'm thinking --"},{"time":97720,"text":"in today's language,\nit would be \"OMG\" or \"WTF.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":101520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105880,"text":"What just happened?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":108240,"text":"So all the confidence\nthat I went in with that morning"},{"time":111880,"text":"was withering away as the morning went on"},{"time":115240,"text":"and the questions kept coming."},{"time":117640,"text":"And at the end of the morning,\nbefore I went home,"},{"time":120200,"text":"the teacher had us in a circle,"},{"time":122160,"text":"and I actually found myself\noutside of the circle."},{"time":124880,"text":"I couldn't look at anybody."},{"time":126240,"text":"I could not understand what just happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130039,"text":"And over the next few years,"},{"time":131960,"text":"I hated to go out in public."},{"time":134080,"text":"I felt every stare, every giggle,"},{"time":137000,"text":"every pointed finger,"},{"time":138680,"text":"not the finger,"},{"time":140120,"text":"but every pointed finger,"},{"time":142080,"text":"and I hated it."},{"time":143360,"text":"I would hide behind my parents' legs\nlike nobody could see me."},{"time":147200,"text":"And as a child,"},{"time":148600,"text":"you can't understand\nanother child's curiosity,"},{"time":151960,"text":"nor an adult's ignorance."},{"time":154680,"text":"It became very apparent to me\nthat the real world was not built"},{"time":159040,"text":"for someone of my size,\nboth literally or figuratively."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164200,"text":"And so I have no anonymity,\nas you can probably tell,"},{"time":169800,"text":"and while you can see my size,"},{"time":171560,"text":"we all go through many challenges\nthrough our lifetime."},{"time":175080,"text":"And some you can see, like mine."},{"time":178080,"text":"Most you can't."},{"time":179680,"text":"You can't tell if someone's dealing\nwith a mental illness,"},{"time":184680,"text":"or they're struggling\nwith their gender identity,"},{"time":187280,"text":"they're caring for an aging parent,"},{"time":189840,"text":"they're having financial difficulty."},{"time":191600,"text":"You can't see that kind of stuff."},{"time":194560,"text":"So while you can see"},{"time":196400,"text":"one of my challenges is my size,"},{"time":199240,"text":"seeing does not mean you understand"},{"time":201600,"text":"what it's truly to be me on a daily basis,\nor what I go through."},{"time":206440,"text":"And so I'm here to debunk a myth."},{"time":208920,"text":"I do not believe you can\nwalk in someone else's shoes,"},{"time":213080,"text":"and because of that, we must adopt\na new way of giving of ourselves."},{"time":217720,"text":"Simply stated, I will never know\nwhat it's like to be you"},{"time":221640,"text":"and you will never know\nwhat it's like to be me."},{"time":224480,"text":"I cannot face your fears\nor chase your dreams,"},{"time":227280,"text":"and you can't do that for me,"},{"time":229160,"text":"but we can be supportive of each other."},{"time":232360,"text":"Instead of trying to walk\nin each other's shoes,"},{"time":235000,"text":"we must adopt a new way\nof giving of ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239440,"text":"I learned at an early age"},{"time":241320,"text":"that I did have to do some things\ndifferent than most people,"},{"time":245200,"text":"but I also learned there were things\nI was on equal footing with,"},{"time":248680,"text":"and one of those was the classroom."},{"time":250840,"text":"Heh, heh, heh. I was equal."},{"time":253960,"text":"As a matter of fact,\nI excelled in the classroom."},{"time":256920,"text":"This was vitally important,\nI discovered as I grew older"},{"time":260519,"text":"and realized I wasn't going to be able\nto do a physical job."},{"time":263840,"text":"I needed an education."},{"time":266240,"text":"So I went on and got a university degree,"},{"time":269200,"text":"but I felt to be one step ahead\nof everyone for employment,"},{"time":273000,"text":"I needed to have\nan advanced university degree,"},{"time":276240,"text":"so I went ahead and got that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277680,"text":"Now I'm ready for my interview."},{"time":279600,"text":"Remember your first interview?\nWhat am I going to wear?"},{"time":282480,"text":"What questions?"},{"time":283720,"text":"And don't forget that firm handshake."},{"time":286040,"text":"I was right there with you."},{"time":287800,"text":"So 24 hours before my interview,"},{"time":289840,"text":"a friend of mine\nwho I've known all my life"},{"time":292400,"text":"called and said, \"Michele,\nthe building you're going in has steps.\""},{"time":296720,"text":"And she knew I couldn't climb steps."},{"time":298920,"text":"So suddenly, my focus changed."},{"time":300800,"text":"In my shoes, I was worried\nabout how am I going to get there?"},{"time":305120,"text":"So I went early and found a loading dock\nand got in and had a great interview."},{"time":310600,"text":"They had no idea what I went through\nfor the day and that's OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314480,"text":"You're probably thinking my greatest\nchallenge that day was the interview,"},{"time":318000,"text":"or getting in the building."},{"time":319920,"text":"In reality, my biggest challenge that day"},{"time":322560,"text":"was getting through the loading dock\nwithout getting run over."},{"time":326200,"text":"I am very vulnerable\nin certain situations:"},{"time":330000,"text":"airports, hallways, parking lots,"},{"time":334320,"text":"loading docks."},{"time":336080,"text":"And so I have to be very careful."},{"time":338120,"text":"I have to anticipate and be flexible"},{"time":341080,"text":"and move as quickly as I can sometimes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344680,"text":"So I got the job,"},{"time":346720,"text":"and in my current role\nI travel quite a bit."},{"time":349800,"text":"And travel is a challenge\nfor all of us these days."},{"time":353280,"text":"And so you probably get to the airport,\nrun through security, get to the gate."},{"time":357640,"text":"Did I get my aisle seat or my window seat?\nDid I get my upgrade?"},{"time":362080,"text":"Me, first of all,\nI don't run through anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":365600,"text":"And I especially don't run through the TSA"},{"time":367680,"text":"because I get to experience\nthe personal patdown."},{"time":371560,"text":"I won't comment on that."},{"time":373360,"text":"And then I make my way to the gate,"},{"time":375360,"text":"and with my gift of gab\nthat my parents said I was born with,"},{"time":379160,"text":"I talk to the gate agent, and then I say,\n\"By the way, my scooter weighs this much,"},{"time":383800,"text":"I have a dry cell battery,"},{"time":385440,"text":"and I can drive it down\nto the door of the plane.\""},{"time":388640,"text":"Also, the day before, I had called\nthe city where I'm traveling to"},{"time":392040,"text":"to find out where I could rent a scooter\nin case mine gets broken on the way."},{"time":397680,"text":"So in my shoes,\nit's a little bit different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400480,"text":"When I get onto the plane,"},{"time":401760,"text":"I use my gift of gab to ask the lady\nto put my bag up, and they graciously do."},{"time":406800,"text":"I try not to eat or drink on a plane"},{"time":408560,"text":"because I don't want to have to\nget up and walk on the plane,"},{"time":411480,"text":"but nature has its own schedule,"},{"time":413080,"text":"and not long ago,\nit knocked and I answered."},{"time":415680,"text":"So I walked up to the front of the plane"},{"time":418080,"text":"and gabbed with the flight attendant,"},{"time":420120,"text":"and said, \"Can you watch the door?\nI can't reach the lock.\""},{"time":424640,"text":"So I'm in there doing my business,\nand the door flies open."},{"time":428440,"text":"And there's a gentleman there"},{"time":430880,"text":"with a look of horror on his face."},{"time":433440,"text":"I'm sure I had the same look."},{"time":435880,"text":"As I came out, I noticed\nthat he was sitting right across from me,"},{"time":441520,"text":"and he's in total, complete embarrassment."},{"time":445120,"text":"So I walk up to him and I quietly go,"},{"time":447840,"text":"\"Are you going to remember this\nas much as I am?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":450160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":456120,"text":"And he goes, \"I think so.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":458120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":459800,"text":"Now, while he's probably\nnot talking about it publicly, I am."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":464960,"text":"But we talked for the rest of the flight,"},{"time":467760,"text":"and we got to know each other,\nour families, sports, work,"},{"time":471680,"text":"and when we landed, he said,"},{"time":473400,"text":"\"Michele, I noticed\nsomeone put your bag up."},{"time":475600,"text":"Can I get that for you?\""},{"time":476840,"text":"And I said, \"Of course, thank you.\""},{"time":479440,"text":"And we wished each other well,"},{"time":481600,"text":"and the most important thing that day"},{"time":483520,"text":"was that he was not going to leave\nwith that embarrassment,"},{"time":487320,"text":"that experience of embarrassment."},{"time":489760,"text":"He won't forget it, and neither will I,"},{"time":492200,"text":"but I think he will remember more"},{"time":494480,"text":"our chat and our different perspectives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498240,"text":"When you travel internationally,"},{"time":500240,"text":"it can be even more challenging\nin certain ways."},{"time":502840,"text":"A few years ago, I was in Zanzibar,"},{"time":505600,"text":"and I come wheeling in,"},{"time":507240,"text":"and think about that."},{"time":509440,"text":"Short, white, blond woman in a chair."},{"time":513919,"text":"That doesn't probably happen every day."},{"time":517360,"text":"So I go up, and with my gift of gab,\nI start to talk to the agent."},{"time":520960,"text":"So friendly, and I ask\nabout their culture and so forth,"},{"time":524400,"text":"and I notice there wasn't a jet bridge."},{"time":527240,"text":"So I had to kind of say,"},{"time":529200,"text":"\"Not only do you have to lift my chair,"},{"time":531280,"text":"I could use some help\ngetting up the steps.\""},{"time":533920,"text":"So we got to spend about an hour together\nwhile we waited for the flight,"},{"time":537800,"text":"and it was the most magnificent hour."},{"time":539680,"text":"Our perspective changed\nfor both of us that day."},{"time":543160,"text":"And once I got on the flight,"},{"time":544600,"text":"he patted me on the back\nand wished me well,"},{"time":547560,"text":"and I thanked him so much."},{"time":549800,"text":"And again, I think he's going\nto remember that experience more"},{"time":554280,"text":"than when I first came in,\nand there was a bit of hesitation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559440,"text":"And as you notice, I get a lot of help."},{"time":561880,"text":"I would not be where I am today"},{"time":563840,"text":"if it was not for my family,\nmy friends, my colleagues"},{"time":568200,"text":"and the many strangers"},{"time":569920,"text":"that help me every single day of my life."},{"time":574040,"text":"And it's important\nthat we all have a support system."},{"time":577880,"text":"Asking for help is a strength,"},{"time":580520,"text":"not a weakness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581760,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":588880,"text":"We all need help throughout our lifetime,"},{"time":591800,"text":"but it is just as important"},{"time":594240,"text":"that we are part\nof other people's support systems."},{"time":597680,"text":"We must adopt that way of giving back."},{"time":600880,"text":"We all obviously have a role to play\nin our own successes,"},{"time":605600,"text":"but think about the role we have to play\nin other people's successes,"},{"time":609200,"text":"just like people do for me\nevery single day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614000,"text":"It's vitally important\nthat we help each other,"},{"time":617560,"text":"because society is increasingly\nplacing people in silos"},{"time":624040,"text":"based on biases and ideologies."},{"time":627600,"text":"And we must look past the surface"},{"time":631080,"text":"and be confronted with the truth"},{"time":633240,"text":"that none of us are what you can see."},{"time":636120,"text":"There's more to us than that,"},{"time":638240,"text":"and we're all dealing with things\nthat you cannot see."},{"time":643240,"text":"So living a life free of judgment"},{"time":646240,"text":"allows all of us to share\nthose experiences together"},{"time":650600,"text":"and have a totally different perspective,"},{"time":653680,"text":"just like the couple of people\nI mentioned earlier in my stories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659280,"text":"So remember, the only shoes"},{"time":661600,"text":"you truly can walk in are your own."},{"time":664840,"text":"I cannot walk in yours."},{"time":667280,"text":"I know you can't walk in my size 1s --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":670280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":671400,"text":"but you can try."},{"time":674080,"text":"But we can do something better than that."},{"time":676920,"text":"With compassion,\ncourage and understanding,"},{"time":680800,"text":"we can walk side by side"},{"time":683520,"text":"and support one another,"},{"time":685600,"text":"and think about how society can change"},{"time":688280,"text":"if we all do that"},{"time":689960,"text":"instead of judging\non only what you can see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693960,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695200,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":700920,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}